{"tid":1079000,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人做過斜視手術？","createTime":"2019-03-26T15:39:24.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-24T07:43:57.000Z","uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"f593a134bd7a1cf78cb6f0b69e36e490074fba23","tid":1079000,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:39:24.000Z","msg":"我對眼其實唔係長期鬥哂雞咁<br />\n淨係右邊隻眼轉唔到向右<br />\n有時望另一個位置 眼球就會飄左去另外一邊<br />\n每次同人傾計 我都好驚比人見到我突然鬥雞眼<br />\n有時會被人誤會我望住另外一個人講野<br />\n十分尷尬<br />\n<br />\n由幼稚園開始就check對眼 <br />\n怪我細路仔唔識世界 遮眼唔知為乜<br />\n屋企人又唔撚明遮完有乜用 <br />\n所以好縱容我想遮就遮唔遮就算<br />\n完全察覺唔到原來自己被人感覺對眼有幾異類<br />\n同埋導致左右眼嚴重度數差距大 (右250 左50 遠視)<br />\n有時配眼鏡 度數相差大好容易唔舒服 <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n一直希望做矯正手術<br />\n我有搵過外國醫生check <br />\n因為恰時之間無香港病歴喺手<br />\n佢叫我去神經科check完先確認做手術<br />\n如果乜都要check多一次<br />\n倒不如我喺香港用返自己舊病歴睇下有無得醫<br />\n<br />\n所以想請問一下有無巴絲打知道呢類手術喺香港<br />\n費用幾多？無論公家又好私家都好<br />\n<br />\n我知公家要等到白髮如雪先做到<br />\n不過想比較下個費用相差大唔大<br />\n跪求有好心人解答<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5d246bf0c4e1a0c514a10dd66b5d6a05a39395a4","tid":1079000,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"咩叫遮眼"},{"pid":"7faf9c2add005765a8d18859c240a41539ced32c","tid":1079000,"uid":77220,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"笑死"},{"pid":"5fea89f23c4beca20cf79f9cfb5a8a6d33b7ed42","tid":1079000,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5d246bf0c4e1a0c514a10dd66b5d6a05a39395a4","tid":1079000,"uid":70183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:41:30.000Z","msg":"咩叫遮眼"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:42:50.000Z","msg":"類似一種物理治療方式<br />\n8歲前 遮住比較健全既眼球去逼轉弱既眼球郁動"},{"pid":"6871a0b273b54e3da08dbe2e6bc7057823a62117","tid":1079000,"uid":11731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"細個已經知道自己斜視，有去公立定期覆診<br />\n最後成20歲仔先做，做完好正常"},{"pid":"5f662787750dffb8036aa715c5510c6138b9d73e","tid":1079000,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7faf9c2add005765a8d18859c240a41539ced32c","tid":1079000,"uid":77220,"like":2,"dislike":4,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:42:07.000Z","msg":"笑死"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:43:29.000Z","msg":"唔好笑我 我好撚慘架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n仲要比人屈我隻眼癱左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3515e9663e792f7e018e17f959968272ed7f3592","tid":1079000,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6871a0b273b54e3da08dbe2e6bc7057823a62117","tid":1079000,"uid":11731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:43:12.000Z","msg":"細個已經知道自己斜視，有去公立定期覆診<br />\n最後成20歲仔先做，做完好正常"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:44:25.000Z","msg":"想問巴打喺邊做？ 費用幾多？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33b3fc81828e55610356daa03c501ebdb0ab1466","tid":1079000,"uid":193601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"細細個就有 7歲就去咗做 好似係聯合做 做完正常返不過就多咗散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3426058323f08941780c8cee62e3342a0af26c1e","tid":1079000,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"33b3fc81828e55610356daa03c501ebdb0ab1466","tid":1079000,"uid":193601,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:48:13.000Z","msg":"細細個就有 7歲就去咗做 好似係聯合做 做完正常返不過就多咗散光<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"絲打係鬥雞定？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a5801138b5ce2dcbf616420944baf78e10b595f","tid":1079000,"uid":20592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:53:39.000Z","msg":"小學開始外斜視 <br />\n得返一隻眼可以對焦到<br />\n無距離感 (EG 斟水隻杯如果成水平向方望會斟唔到..)<br />\n長期左眼望野結果左眼近視+散光成千, 右眼幾百<br />\n但右眼因長期唔用有弱視, CHECK過得80~90%視力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n細個老豆老母定期覆下診無做手術結果不了了之<br />\n<br />\n去到E家成25歲想去私家做 養和好似要成4-5萬蚊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6225d4b437cfd79a3e7fd77194834fdadb441904","tid":1079000,"uid":91936,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:55:36.000Z","msg":"做過<br />\n排期排咗年半睇<br />\n原本之後要排多年做手術<br />\n咁啱醫院有個期突咗<br />\n排咗幾個禮拜都唔使就做咗<br />\n<br />\n做完手術第一日你係開唔到對眼<br />\n第二日先開到 不過睇嘢好矇<br />\n對眼好紅 會標眼水<br />\n跟住慢慢就好翻<br />\n<br />\n同埋做之前醫生會問你做一隻定兩隻眼<br />\n建議做兩隻 會無咁痛"},{"pid":"361e1cfbadb52599e85599f8951f1fb7fedb8691","tid":1079000,"uid":5793,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-26T15:55:59.000Z","msg":"我依家兩隻眼可以好似變色龍咁無定向扭黎扭去<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"39acb5a864e1daab3b3129b9e81678aefb3631cf","tid":1079000,"uid":109251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"361e1cfbadb52599e85599f8951f1fb7fedb8691","tid":1079000,"uid":5793,"lik